{"tid":422954,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"開價$2,598起，雙鏡中階 Galaxy C8 本週上市！","createTime":"2017-10-03T13:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T07:13:57.000Z","uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"94ec399266d6901fdd9dfb36adc45bab8515fa03","tid":422954,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mobilesetting.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Galaxy-C8-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilesetting.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FGalaxy-C8-1.jpg&h=8268049a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamsung 的 Galaxy C系列向來在香港一向都大受歡迎，不過對上一款 Galaxy C9 Pro 推出已接近一年，應該係時候有後繼機出現，Samsung 香港今日宣佈將雙鏡中階版&nbsp; Galaxy C8 帶到香港。Galaxy C8 是&nbsp;Samsung 旗下第三款雙鏡手機，該機與早前發佈的 Galaxy J7+ 功能幾乎一致，同樣採用全金屬一體設計，備有5.5寸 1080p Super AMOLED 屏幕，搭載1300萬像素+500萬雙鏡頭等，備有黑、金及粉紅三色。Galaxy C8 建議零售價為$2,598(32GB版) 及 $2,998(64GB版)，並於10月6日上市。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n外觀方面，Galaxy&nbsp;C8採用了全金屬機身與以往的 Galaxy C系列風格相近，不過最大的分別是該機採用直排放置的雙鏡像頭，而且還可以拍攝後對焦。至於在拍攝方面，Galaxy&nbsp;C8 搭載了一枚1300萬像 CMOS F/1.7大光圈及一枚 500萬像 F/1.9光圈的鏡頭。自拍鏡頭為1600萬像(F/1.9光圈) ，並支援實時背景虛化等功能。在其他規格方面，該機只配備 MTK Helio P25 處理器，3GB RAM + 32GB ROM 及 4GB RAM + 64GB ROM，電池容量為3000mAh。此外，Galaxy C8 還加入了 Bixby、Always on、Multi Window、前置指紋識別及臉部識別等功能。"},{"pid":"f237c4e433f468ec46230461c4d1deaf91b27f32","tid":422954,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:42:35.000Z","msg":"wa屌mtk<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8589c80594410f7b7cb268486eeb602fbf5188","tid":422954,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"呢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabd751a94be2271e57a83e2129af17bfbb64c93","tid":422954,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"電子垃圾"},{"pid":"2d03f1e512c39475e